text: Jan Hendrikus Cornelis van Zanen (born 4 September 1961) is a Dutch politician. He is a member of the VVD. He has been Mayor of The Hague since 2020. He was Mayor of Utrecht (2014-2020) and Amstelveen (2005-2013) and national chairperson of the VVD (2003-2008). ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Aldermen of the Netherlands Category:Dutch councillors Category:Dutch jurists Category:Dutch mayors Category:Dutch party chairs Category:Mayors of The Hague Category:People from Purmerend Category:People from Amstelveen Category:People's Party for Freedom and Democracy politicians Category:Politicians from North Holland
